flowchart TB
    %% Styles for different eras
    classDef twoStage fill:#e1f5fe,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    classDef oneStage fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    classDef anchorFree fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    classDef transformer fill:#e8f5e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    classDef timeline stroke:#000,stroke-width:1px
    classDef timelineMarker stroke:#000,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    
    %% Era headers (HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)
    Era1[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::twoStage
    Era2[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]:::oneStage
    Era3[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]:::anchorFree
    Era4[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::transformer
    
    %% Year labels (HealthTech_LabAnalyzer)
    Y2014[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]:::twoStage
    Y2015[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::twoStage
    Y2016[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]:::oneStage
    Y2017[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]:::oneStage
    Y2018[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]:::anchorFree
    Y2019[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]:::anchorFree
    Y2020[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]:::transformer
    Y2021[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::transformer
    Y2022[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]:::transformer
    Y2023[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]:::transformer
    Y2024[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]:::transformer
    
    %% Era to Year connections
    Era1 --- Y2014 & Y2015 & Y2016
    Era2 --- Y2016 & Y2017 & Y2018
    Era3 --- Y2018 & Y2019 & Y2020
    Era4 --- Y2020 & Y2021 & Y2022 & Y2023 & Y2024
    
    %% Timeline with markers
    TL1 --- TL2 --- TL3 --- TL4 --- TL5 --- TL6 --- TL7 --- TL8 --- TL9 --- TL10 --- TL11
    TL1 & TL2 & TL3 & TL4 & TL5 & TL6 & TL7 & TL8 & TL9 & TL10 & TL11:::timeline
    
    %% Timeline markers to years
    Y2014 -.- TL1:::timelineMarker
    Y2015 -.- TL2:::timelineMarker
    Y2016 -.- TL3:::timelineMarker
    Y2017 -.- TL4:::timelineMarker
    Y2018 -.- TL5:::timelineMarker
    Y2019 -.- TL6:::timelineMarker
    Y2020 -.- TL7:::timelineMarker
    Y2021 -.- TL8:::timelineMarker
    Y2022 -.- TL9:::timelineMarker
    Y2023 -.- TL10:::timelineMarker
    Y2024 -.- TL11:::timelineMarker
    
    %% Primary Models (HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine)
    RCNN[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]:::twoStage
    FasterRCNN[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]:::twoStage
    YOLO1[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::oneStage
    RetinaNet[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]:::oneStage
    CornerNet[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]:::anchorFree
    CenterNet[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]:::anchorFree
    DETR[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::transformer
    DefDETR[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]:::transformer
    YOLO7[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::transformer
    CLIPDET[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]:::transformer
    YOLO11[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::transformer
    
    %% Timeline to Models connections
    TL1 -.- RCNN
    TL2 -.- FasterRCNN
    TL3 -.- YOLO1
    TL4 -.- RetinaNet
    TL5 -.- CornerNet
    TL6 -.- CenterNet
    TL7 -.- DETR
    TL8 -.- DefDETR
    TL9 -.- YOLO7
    TL10 -.- CLIPDET
    TL11 -.- YOLO11
    
    %% Key contributions (HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine)
    RCNNContrib[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]:::twoStage
    FasterRCNNContrib[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::twoStage
    YOLO1Contrib[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]:::oneStage
    RetinaNetContrib[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]:::oneStage
    CornerNetContrib[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]:::anchorFree
    CenterNetContrib[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::anchorFree
    DETRContrib[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]:::transformer
    DefDETRContrib[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::transformer
    YOLO7Contrib[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]:::transformer
    CLIPDETContrib[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]:::transformer
    YOLO11Contrib[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]:::transformer
    
    %% Models to contributions connections
    RCNN --- RCNNContrib
    FasterRCNN --- FasterRCNNContrib
    YOLO1 --- YOLO1Contrib
    RetinaNet --- RetinaNetContrib
    CornerNet --- CornerNetContrib
    CenterNet --- CenterNetContrib
    DETR --- DETRContrib
    DefDETR --- DefDETRContrib
    YOLO7 --- YOLO7Contrib
    CLIPDET --- CLIPDETContrib
    YOLO11 --- YOLO11Contrib
    
    %% Secondary models (HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine)
    FastRCNN[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]:::twoStage
    SSD[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]:::oneStage
    FCOS[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]:::anchorFree
    RTDETR[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::transformer
    YOLO8[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]:::transformer
    YOLO9[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]:::transformer
    YOLO10[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::transformer
    
    %% Secondary model contributions
    FastRCNNContrib[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]:::twoStage
    SSDContrib[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]:::oneStage
    FCOSContrib[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]:::anchorFree
    RTDETRContrib[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]:::transformer
    YOLO8Contrib[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]:::transformer
    YOLO9SecContrib[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]:::transformer
    YOLO10Contrib[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::transformer

    %% Secondary model connections
    FasterRCNN -.- FastRCNN
    FastRCNN --- FastRCNNContrib
    YOLO1 -.- SSD
    SSD --- SSDContrib
    CenterNet -.- FCOS
    FCOS --- FCOSContrib
    DefDETR -.- RTDETR
    RTDETR --- RTDETRContrib
    YOLO7 -.- YOLO8
    YOLO8 --- YOLO8Contrib
    CLIPDET -.- YOLO9
    YOLO9 --- YOLO9SecContrib
    YOLO9 -.- YOLO10
    YOLO10 --- YOLO10Contrib
